    "description": "<strong>Endless Platformer with Side-Scrolling Camera</strong><br>Guide Freya through the harsh winds and cold terrain of the far north, overcome many obstacles and avoid pesky penguins who are trying to stop her!<br><br>Increase Freya's control and movement speed by knocking down penguins and saving reindeer. These also contribute to your total Dreampoints.<br><br>Reach new stages by gathering Dreampoints,<br><strong>BE WARNED!</strong><br>Higher stages increase the speed of the storm chasing you!<br>Higher stages also requires more precise movement and planning.<br><br><strong>Some of the obstacles you will be facing are:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spikes<br></li><li>Poisonous flowers<br></li><li>Rotating platforms<br></li><li>Vertical/horizontal platforms<br></li><li>Falling platforms</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832150/extras/df2c62bf7790bbf5b0c1953b1578a770.poster.avif?t=1723773126\" width=570 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832150/extras/df2c62bf7790bbf5b0c1953b1578a770.webm?t=1723773126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832150/extras/df2c62bf7790bbf5b0c1953b1578a770.mp4?t=1723773126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Crushing pillars<br></li><li>Flying penguins</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832150/extras/5fb4c2e360adf929ff36ab23c6a74319.poster.avif?t=1723773126\" width=570 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832150/extras/5fb4c2e360adf929ff36ab23c6a74319.webm?t=1723773126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/